---
title: "Achieving Fairness with a Simple Ridge Penalty"
collection: publications
permalink: /publication/fair_ridge
authors: 'Marco Scutari, Francesca Panero, Manuel Proissl'
excerpt: 'In this paper we present a general framework for estimating regression models subject to a user-defined level of fairness. We do that using ridge regression, which is flexible, has already tons of literature and in general simplifies a lot the estimation.'
date: 2021-04-01
venue: 'Statistics and Computing, to appear'
link: 'https://arxiv.org/abs/2105.13817.pdf'
